msgid "300:部屋の主である西條拓巳――タクは、今はここにはいない。扉の鍵はかかっていなくて、簡単に侵入できた。"
msgstr "300:The room's owner, Takumi Nishijo, was nowhere to be seen. The door hadn't been locked, so she'd been able to walk right in."

msgid "400:梨深はケータイで時間を確かめる。午後１０時少し前。[%p]"
msgstr "400:Rimi looked at the time on her phone. It was a little before 10:00 PM.[%p]"

msgid "500:――まだタクは、スクランブル交差点にいるのかな。[%p]"
msgstr "500:She wondered if Taku was still at Scramble Crossing.[%p]"

msgid "600:できれば助けに行きたかった。実際に助けに行こうとした。[%p]"
msgstr "600:She'd wanted to go to help him. She'd tried, in fact.[%p]"

msgid "700:だがスクランブル交差点に近づこうとすればするほど、人の数は多くなっていって、ついにはほとんど身動きが取れないような状況になった。[%p]"
msgstr "700:But the crush of people in Scramble Crossing was so intense that she'd barely been able to move.[%p]"

msgid "800:結局、Ｏ－ＦＲＯＮＴにたどり着く前に“エスパー少年のショー”は終わってしまい、それと時を同じくして、タクミからの声が聞こえてきたのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "800:The “Boy Psychic Show” ended before she could get to O-FRONT, and just as it had ended, she'd heard Takumi's voice.[%p]"

msgid "900:七海の手首を取り戻してきてほしい、という懇願。[%p]"
msgstr "900:He wanted her to get Nanami's hand back.[%p]"

msgid "1000:タクミが梨深になにかを頼んでくるなんて、珍しいことだった。[linebreak]七海は今、ＮＯＺＯＭＩに連れ去られて酷い目に遭わされている。タクミは思考盗撮の末に、その事実を突き止めていた。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:It was rare for Takumi to ask Rimi for something. Nanami had been kidnapped by NOZOMI, and right now, they were doing horrible things to her. Takumi's mind-reading had shown him that much.[%p]"

msgid "1100:梨深も七海とは過去に面識があったから、それを知ったときには胸が張り裂けそうな想いだった。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:Rimi had known Nanami in the past, and hearing this made her heart feel like it would burst.[%p]"

msgid "1200:ソファの上に置かれた段ボール。その中に収められている、手首と、七海のケータイと、かわいらしいバングル。[linebreak]それを見て、梨深は言葉を失ってしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:There was a cardboard box on the sofa. Inside was a human hand, Nanami's phone, and a cute little bangle. When she saw it, Rimi fell speechless.[%p]"

msgid "1300:悔しくて、悲しくて、七海が心配で。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:She was sad, frustrated, and worried about Nanami.[%p]"

msgid "1400:そして同時に、かつて自分が味わった苦しみの記憶が、頭の中でフラッシュバックしてきて。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:And at the same time, the memories of what she'd suffered in the past came flashing back to her.[%p]"

msgid "1500:梨深はきつく唇を噛み、その手首をしばらくの間、見つめ続けた。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:She bit her lip and spent a while staring at the severed hand.[%p]"

msgid "1600:一度深く深呼吸して、なんとか落ち着きを取り戻すと、段ボールのふたをそっと閉める。ガムテープでしっかりと封をしてから、脇に抱えて部屋を出た。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:She took a single deep breath to calm herself down, and then closed the box's lid. After resealing it tightly with masking tape, she put it under her arm and left the room.[%p]"

msgid "1700:ケータイを取り出し、ワンセグでテレビに繋ぐ。[linebreak]ついさっきまで、スクランブル交差点からの生中継をやっていた。それを確認したかった。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:She took out her phone and used its built-in TV tuner. A moment ago, they'd been doing a live broadcast from Scramble Crossing. She'd wanted to see it.[%p]"

msgid "1800:けれど、該当するチャンネルに合わせても、延々とＣＭが流れ続けるだけ。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:But all the channels were showing nothing but commercials.[%p]"

msgid "1900:どうやら生中継は終わってしまったらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:The live broadcast must have ended.[%p]"

msgid "2000:ということは、タクはもうあのスクランブル交差点にはいないだろう。[linebreak]やむなく梨深はタクミのいる、いつもの病室へ戻るしかなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "2000:Taku probably wasn't at Scramble Crossing anymore, then. With nothing else to do, Rimi headed back to the room where Takumi waited.[%p]"

msgid "2100:明かりが消されて、暗いままの病室。[linebreak]タクミはいつものように、ベッドではなく車イスに腰掛けていた。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:The lights were off, and the room was dark. Like always, Takumi was in his wheelchair, not his bed.[%p]"

msgid "2200:[name]タクミ[line]「七海の腕は……？」[%p]"
msgstr "2200:[name]タクミ[line]Do you have Nanami's hand?[%p]"

msgid "2300:[name]梨深[line]「うん。持ってきた」[%p]"
msgstr "2300:[name]梨深[line]Yeah. I brought it.[%p]"

msgid "2400:梨深はそれが入った段ボールを、タクミに差し出す。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:She handed him the box.[%p]"

msgid "2500:[name]タクミ[line]「ありがとう」[%p]"
msgstr "2500:[name]タクミ[line]Thank you.[%p]"

msgid "2600:[name]梨深[line]「治せるかな？\u3000治せるよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "2600:[name]梨深[line]Can they reattach it? They can, right?[%p]"

msgid "2700:[name]タクミ[line]「分からない……。でもこの病院なら、冷凍保存しておける設備がある」[%p]"
msgstr "2700:[name]タクミ[line]I don't know, but this hospital has a cold storage system.[%p]"

msgid "2800:ただ放置しておくよりは、冷凍保存する方がずっとマシだろう。[linebreak]それでも治る保証なんてまったくない。[linebreak]“彼”が暗にそう言っているように思えて――[%p]"
msgstr "2800:It would be a lot better to keep it cold, rather than just leave it to rot, but there was no guarantee they could ever reattach it. She felt like that's what he was trying to tell her.[%p]"

msgid "2900:[name]梨深[line]「大丈夫。きっと、治るよ」[%p]"
msgstr "2900:[name]梨深[line]Don't worry. They'll be able to fix it.[%p]"

msgid "3000:梨深はあえて、前向きなことを口にした。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:Rimi decided to be optimistic.[%p]"

msgid "3100:[name]梨深[line]「きっと治るって、信じる」[%p]"
msgstr "3100:[name]梨深[line]She'll be okay. I believe it.[%p]"

msgid "3200:[name]梨深[line]「もっとも、その前に、七海ちゃんを助け出さなきゃいけないけど」[%p]"
msgstr "3200:[name]梨深[line]Of course, we have to get her back, first.[%p]"

msgid "3300:[name]タクミ[line]「……七海は殺されることはないと思う。焦って動くことはないよ」[%p]"
msgstr "3300:[name]タクミ[line]I don't think she'll be killed. We don't need to rush.[%p]"

msgid "3400:[name]梨深[line]「冷静なんだね」[%p]"
msgstr "3400:[name]梨深[line]You're pretty calm right now.[%p]"

msgid "3500:[name]タクミ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "3500:[name]タクミ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "3600:[name]梨深[line]「……ごめん。今言った言葉は、忘れて」[%p]"
msgstr "3600:[name]梨深[line]Sorry. Just forget I said that.[%p]"

msgid "3700:[name]梨深[line]「それより、タクは今どこにいるか、分かる？」[%p]"
msgstr "3700:[name]梨深[line]Anyway, do you know where Taku is?[%p]"

msgid "3800:[name]タクミ[line]「この病院に搬送されてきたよ。精神科の病室で眠ってる」[%p]"
msgstr "3800:[name]タクミ[line]He was brought to this hospital. He's asleep in the psych ward.[%p]"

msgid "3900:[name]梨深[line]「そうなの！？」[%p]"
msgstr "3900:[name]梨深[line]Really?[%p]"

msgid "4000:梨深は目を丸くすると、すぐさま病室を飛び出していた。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:Rimi's eyes went wide, and she ran out of the room.[%p]"

msgid "4100:すでに面会時間が過ぎて照明が落とされた廊下を、足音を忍ばせて歩く。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:The hospital was closed to visitors, and the lights were turned down. She walked softly down the hallways as she went.[%p]"

msgid "4200:この病院のスタッフに、ＮＯＺＯＭＩや天成神光会の関係者がいることは、すでに知っていた。だから目立つ行動はできない。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:She already knew that people from NOZOMI and the Cosmic Church of the Divine Light had infiltrated the hospital's staff. She couldn't do anything that would attract attention.[%p]"

msgid "4300:タクミから教えてもらった病室にたどり着くと、周囲に誰もいないことを確かめてから、梨深はゆっくりとドアを開いた。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:When she got to the room Takumi had told her about, she made sure there was nobody inside before slowly opening the door.[%p]"

msgid "4400:そこは内装が白で統一された、温かみがこれっぽっちもない部屋だった。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:The room's furnishings and walls were a solid white, without a trace of warmth to them.[%p]"

msgid "4500:梨深は音もなく、中央のベッドに歩み寄った。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:Rimi soundlessly walked over to the bed.[%p]"

msgid "4600:そこで、タクが眠っていた。苦しげに眉根を寄せ、たまにうめき声を漏らしている。額は汗でびっしょりだ。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:Taku was sleeping there. His brow was furrowed as if he was in pain, and occasionally he would moan. His forehead was damp with sweat.[%p]"

msgid "4700:梨深はそんなタクの頬を、そっと撫でて――[%p]"
msgstr "4700:Rimi softly stroked his cheek.[%p]"

msgid "4800:[name]梨深[line]「ごめんね、あなたを、守ってあげられなくて」[%p]"
msgstr "4800:[name]梨深[line]I'm sorry I couldn't protect you.[%p]"

msgid "4900:いたたまれない気持ちで、そうつぶやいていた。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:She whispered sadly.[%p]"

